@startuml 09_PlatformAbstraction
!theme plain
title Ruffnova - 平台抽象层时序图

participant "AppState" as State
participant "RuffleBridge" as Bridge

box "macOS Platform" #LightYellow
    participant "MacInputProvider" as MacInput
    participant "MacFilePickerService" as MacPicker
    participant "MacMenuLocalization\nService" as MacMenu
    participant "RuffleMetalView\nMacOS" as MacView
    participant "NSOpenPanel" as NSPanel
    participant "NSWindow" as NSWin
end box

box "iOS Platform" #LightBlue
    participant "IOSInputProvider" as IOSInput
    participant "IOSFilePickerService" as IOSPicker
    participant "RuffleMetalView\nIOS" as IOSView
    participant "UIDocumentPicker\nViewController" as UIDoc
    participant "IOSOrientation\nController" as IOSOrient
end box

== macOS 输入事件 ==

MacView -> MacView : NSEvent mouseDown/moved/up
MacView -> MacInput : sendMouseDown(x, y, button)
MacInput -> Bridge : sendMouseEvent(x, y, type=1, delta=0)
Bridge -> Bridge : ruffle_player_mouse_event FFI

MacView -> MacView : NSEvent keyDown
MacView -> MacInput : sendKeyDown(keyCode, charCode, modifiers)
MacInput -> Bridge : sendKeyEvent(keyCode, charCode, true, mods)
Bridge -> Bridge : ruffle_player_key_event FFI

== iOS 输入事件 ==

IOSView -> IOSView : UITapGestureRecognizer
IOSView -> IOSInput : sendTap(x, y)
IOSInput -> IOSInput : sendMouseDown + sendMouseUp
IOSInput -> Bridge : sendMouseEvent FFI

IOSView -> IOSView : UILongPressGestureRecognizer
IOSView -> IOSInput : sendLongPress(x, y)
IOSInput -> Bridge : sendMouseEvent(x, y, type=3)\n映射为右键

== macOS 文件选择 ==

State -> MacPicker : pickSWFFile(completion:)
MacPicker -> NSPanel : NSOpenPanel()\n.allowedContentTypes = [.swf]
NSPanel -> NSPanel : runModal()
NSPanel --> MacPicker : selected URL
MacPicker --> State : completion(url)

== iOS 文件选择 ==

State -> IOSPicker : pickSWFFile(completion:)
IOSPicker -> UIDoc : UIDocumentPickerViewController\n(for: [.swf])
IOSPicker -> IOSPicker : 找到 topViewController
IOSPicker -> UIDoc : present(animated)
UIDoc --> IOSPicker : documentPicker(didPickDocumentsAt:)
IOSPicker --> State : completion(url)

== macOS 菜单本地化 ==

State -> MacMenu : apply() [on .localizationChanged]
MacMenu -> MacMenu : NSApp.mainMenu\n遍历所有菜单项
MacMenu -> MacMenu : canonicalTopLevelKey / canonicalItemKey\n映射到 localization key
MacMenu -> MacMenu : locManager.localized(key)\n替换菜单标题

== iOS 屏幕方向控制 ==

State -> IOSOrient : update(orientation)
IOSOrient -> IOSOrient : supportedOrientations = orientation
IOSOrient -> IOSOrient : windowScene\n.requestGeometryUpdate()

note over State
  AppState 根据 SWF 舞台尺寸决定方向:
  - 宽 > 高 → .landscape
  - 高 > 宽 → .portrait
end note

== 协议抽象 ==

note over MacInput, IOSInput
  **InputProvider Protocol**
  ├── sendMouseMove(x, y)
  ├── sendMouseDown/Up(x, y, button)
  ├── sendScroll(x, y, deltaX, deltaY)
  ├── sendKeyDown/Up(keyCode, charCode, modifiers)
  ├── sendTap(x, y)
  ├── sendDoubleTap(x, y)
  └── sendLongPress(x, y)

  **FilePickerService Protocol**
  ├── pickSWFFile(completion:)
  ├── pickFolder(completion:)
  └── saveScreenshot(data, name, completion:)
end note

@enduml
